{"pageProps":{"postContent":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"日前，LS 發現了 leaague 遊戲中一個關於他的彩蛋：在商店中搜尋 \"ls\" 或是 \"last shadow\"時，搜尋結果會出現 Liandry's Anguish 與 Morellonomicon 兩個道具。當下，他立刻激動無比，幾近哽咽。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":167},"end":{"line":11,"column":125,"offset":291}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":"","url":"immortal_1.png","alt":"TODO"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"要了解這件事的來由需要一些背景知識：LS, aka \"Last Shadow\"，知名 League of Legends 分析師/ 教練/ 評論家。一度面臨收入危機時因業餘 league 教學影片獲得巨大反響得到歐洲戰隊 Supa Hot Crew 教練職位，之後活躍於 league 電競業界至今。執教風格為追求低風險與無失誤，推崇「完美的正規打法」。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":314},"end":{"line":15,"column":178,"offset":491}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"LS 與上述兩個道具的淵源來自他依照裝備數據計算 Morellonomicon 的 c/p 值過低，多次提倡合成前置裝備的 Oblivion Orb 之後購買 Liandry's Torment 的打法才能獲得最大傷害/金錢效益。他屢次在比賽評論時激進提倡購買 Liandry，排斥 Morello 的行為塑造了強烈的個人形象，也成為 league 玩家社群的迷因。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":493},"end":{"line":17,"column":184,"offset":676}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我看到這件新聞時第一個閃過腦內的單字是 \"legacy\"。事實上，作為獨立起家的遊戲，league 早期為獎勵玩家邀請朋友，提供了「使用帳號專屬連結邀請一千人，遊戲內一個道具將以自己遊戲內名稱命名」的獎勵。許多玩家因此留名於遊戲內。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":678},"end":{"line":19,"column":117,"offset":794}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"但除此以外，因對 league 的貢獻而能在遊戲中留名的寥寥可數。對 LS 致敬的這個彩蛋是他在這個遊戲留下的 legacy。就像是 ","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1,"offset":796},"end":{"line":21,"column":68,"offset":863}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://wowwiki-archive.fandom.com/wiki/Red_Shirt_Guy","children":[{"type":"text","value":"WOW 的紅衣歷史學家","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":69,"offset":864},"end":{"line":21,"column":80,"offset":875}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":68,"offset":863},"end":{"line":21,"column":136,"offset":931}}},{"type":"text","value":"。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":136,"offset":931},"end":{"line":21,"column":137,"offset":932}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"LS 本人則是在自己的","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":934},"end":{"line":23,"column":12,"offset":945}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EM1oFg5QY9o","children":[{"type":"text","value":"youtube 影片","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":13,"offset":946},"end":{"line":23,"column":23,"offset":956}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":12,"offset":945},"end":{"line":23,"column":69,"offset":1002}}},{"type":"text","value":"用了 \"immortalized\" 這個字。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":69,"offset":1002},"end":{"line":23,"column":91,"offset":1024}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/Refer-A-Friend","children":[{"type":"text","value":"LOL fandom wiki 的 refer-a-friend 頁面","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":92,"offset":1025},"end":{"line":23,"column":127,"offset":1060}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":91,"offset":1024},"end":{"line":23,"column":184,"offset":1117}}},{"type":"text","value":"也使用了同一個字。原來如此。職業會結束，生命會結束，但留存於遊戲內的記錄是不朽的。常聽說「人在被遺忘時才真正死亡」，當你留名史上得以使後人瞻仰時，你便永遠不會被遺忘 — 因此達成了永生。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":184,"offset":1117},"end":{"line":23,"column":277,"offset":1210}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"所謂的不朽，並非怪力亂神，或只存在於教科書中。也不是說以如此規模留名是件簡單的事，但確實更新了我對 \"immortal\" 一字的認知。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":1212},"end":{"line":25,"column":68,"offset":1279}}}]}],"postSummary":{"id":"immortal","title":"Immortal","category":"League of Legends","language":["zh-TW"],"tags":[],"publishDate":"2021-03-12","pathname":"immortal","zhTwLink":null,"filename":"Immortal (blog)"}},"__N_SSG":true}